item.title: CVE-2024-45309|2024-10-21T14:55:18.293Z -- theonedev -- onedev
item.description: OneDev is a Git server with CI/CD, kanban, and packages. A vulnerability in versions prior to 11.0.9 allows unauthenticated users to read arbitrary files accessible by the OneDev server process. This issue has been fixed in version 11.0.9.
